data.horoscope_data: Clarity won’t be so clear over the next couple of weeks now that Neptune is in Aries and your communication zone. This dreamy aspect puts everything in a haze so we can’t tell fact from fiction. Learn to use your intuition, Aquarius, because it might know something you don’t.Stick to your budget when Saturn in Pisces sextiles Uranus in Taurus on Friday. Creating structured spending habits can help you land the home of your dreams. From shopping for a new home to moving to a new city, starting a savings plan can help you reach your goal.End the week on a creative note when the sun in Aries sextiles Jupiter in Gemini on Sunday. You’ll have a powerful urge to express yourself, so use this energy to work on creative projects or update your personal style. Be unique and stand out from the crowd. Enjoy!
